entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued June 01 at 8:54AM AKDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...INCREASED FIRE DANGER FOR THE REMAINDER OF THIS WEEK... Conditions remain dry across Southeast Alaska and temperatures will continue to rise to the upper 70s and lower 80s across much of the region over the next few days.
